title: Steeler - Metal Generation _ The Anthology
description:
Music : Rock : Other quality




This CD is a mixture of rare and unreleased material that neatly tells the full story of the Ron Keel fronted band that ripped the LA club scene up in the early to mid eighties. With sleeve notes by Ron himself, a selection of rare photos and even some live Malmsteen era material, there's a lot on offer.
